Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b0\bord5\blur10\fs65\3c&H482ABA&\4c&H482ABA&\pos(1144.8,140)}Translated & timed by saalow\Nencoding by FreshUdon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, unfortunately, we have some sad news
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To share with all the viewers at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Housei-kun has been a regular on this program
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaki no Tsukai ya Arahende, since our second episode
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...and he's been gibing it his best shot since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Housei-kun has, after much thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Decided to move on from the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's talk that he may leave the industry altogether,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've heard that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Might just be a rumor, but it seems he's made his mind up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Without further ado, allow us to bring out the man himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukitei Housei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, a word or two on why you've come to this decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A reason for your retirement, because we're not quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite clear on why you've gotta abandon showbiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So an explanation would be appreciated if possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...an explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already 50 years old, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So much has happened, so much, and so I quit comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And now intend to singularly devote myself to reproducing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to have children!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's certainly no reason to quit, though. You cold make that work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife, her name's Aya, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She just turned 40 and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's just so beautiful, such a beautiful woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an exquisite woman, my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He leers at ther and makes the most horrid faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I bring her up in conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When we went drinking the other night,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You seemed weirdly interested in how my sex life was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well I don't quite recall asking about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd had quite a bit to drink after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So I apologize for offending you. That wasn't my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If my actions at all influenced your decision to retire,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's on me and I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So just to confirm,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not leaving the program, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving the entertainment industry {\i1}entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...and, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reasoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd love to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka, why is it, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That I've decided to quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I mean, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I don't want you to quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel that if you don't have a clear reason to leave
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should give this decision a little bit more thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for you to quit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you would reconsider this choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right, maybe give it another shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What bliss...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the way it must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we'd like to present a selection of \Nfamous scenes curated by Housei-kun himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please roll the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukitei Housei, 50 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1229.325,311.2)}Narrated by Ashida Mana
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Appearing on {\i1}Gaki no Tsukai{\i0} since its second episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Housei-kun has made his mark in dozens of memorable skits,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And is now retiring from the world of comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, we look back on all the joy he has given us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At number 5, Yamazaki vs. Jimmy:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Blood Feud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's  your problem, dick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a screw loose or something, dumbass?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no greater enemy for little Housei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:05:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,None other than his Yoshimoto senpai, Jimmy Onish-san
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever they crossed paths, a bloodbath ensued.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back at the two of them, one can't help but feel nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you're an annoying little fucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that's annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinkin' you're such hot shit with this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU DOING
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a dumbass like you would drive this piece of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who you calling a dumbass, dumbass?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,With your dumbass clothes and your dumbass car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 4, Yamasaki vs. Moriman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimmy wasn't the only villain in Housei's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that very personage responsible for so many great fights:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Moriman-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(751.95,820.4)}BURDOCK BEATDOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That got him in the face just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit right in the face with a burdock root.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A burdock root... is just a stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 3: Yamasaki, Music Producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, I still remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiming for a lifetime of royalties,\NThis song, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Housei embarked on composing hiw own pop music,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And completed a catalog of 20 original songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bid farewell this evening with a very special performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:07:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah~ Yamasaki-san The star filled sky we gazed upon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Still rings in my heart as if it were yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah~ Matsumoto-san The promise we made on that day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep it in my heart because it's precious to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah~ Tanaka-san Did you find what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you'll find a way to make your heart whole
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah~ Endo-san In your room, you told me of a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you nodded and smiled, I'll never forget that kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just out of reach, so close yet so far
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Those stars that shine so brightly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, always, take us in your arms
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For we are far too weak
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At number 2, Yama no Ishimatsu: Slayer of 100 Men
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the situation, you were always up for a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For your 20th anniversary in the business,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You shought to cut down 100 men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle went smoothly at first, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your strength was gradually sapped by your enemie's attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada's mean streak is peeking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, he tried to run away, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, Hamada-san, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really showing your worst qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You fled from the set.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You ain't gotta cry like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My back hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on we'll wait until you attack us to go after you, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- We promise, we promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you calling y--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 1, Yamasaki's Moving Wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Again with this? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, how many times do we have to watch this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Always childlike, our little rascal finally tied the knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You selflessly allowed us to share in your joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like some sort of "How To Get Married" video.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this weirdly high production value?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... that kind of high quality you don't see on TV, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened that made you cry like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Housei-kun, we watched you grow up alongside the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:11:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But the time has finally come for you to end this chapter of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as time goes on, our memories of you will not fade,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For we keep those moments in the albums of our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, for now and for always.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(731.25,781.5)}Farewell
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks for the memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And now for some parting words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She changed jobs in 2014,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Our former receptionist, Uchino.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uchino-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In 2014-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone signed it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever drag me back here for dumb shit like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She came all this way, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(143.425,42.567)}Hell yeah! (manager)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(238.95,81.633)}Stop taking my IPhone charger (AP)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(112.9,121.233)}this rules (Hulu)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(136.2,163.433)}WE DID IT (the ADs)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(172.425,200.4)}disappear (all Yoshimoto)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(154.275,242.7)}Weird body (wardrobe)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(295.25,282.2)}The next time I see you I'll kick your ass (Irie)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(324.025,326.4)}We saw him shoplifting the other day (front desk)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(228.525,363.867)}Your ears are rotting (sound dept.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(238.1,404.3)}Keep your sorry ass in Osaka (NTV)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(247.4,443.4)}A waste of electricity (lightning dept.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We also have a few words we'd like to share,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with Cocorico.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't until last night, actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That I heard you were leaving Gaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I went back home,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to my wife and my mother-in-law, who's in town visiting her grandkid,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and told them the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They were like "Thank God!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Semms like they both really hated your guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're really jazzed about this, so thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I've always hated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We've also prepared some words tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I have know each other for many years, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've never met up outside of work for a meal or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But these days there's tons of people going into retirement
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think any less of them, so, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So yeah, good luck out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, *** and I first met back in...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, that's what Aya's been calling you lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as I was saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This was back in my twenties when *** and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have been about 20, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'l never forget you, ***.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be seeing a lot more of your wife from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be great, ***!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And lastly, from Housei-kun himself, some parting words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That made these flowers bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was five men.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All five of us, together...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They all went away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I dream that suddenly I was alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,AND I WAS SO VERY LONELY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,BUT EVEN THEN
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,EVEN THEN!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I shed no tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But even then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I was the only one from Gaki left...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't cry", said a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm remembering now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That dream, I'm recalling more of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,HAMADA-CHAN WAS THE ONE SPEAKING TO ME
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was him! HAMADA-CHAN, he spoke to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How tragic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whas this how you pictured it would end?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In all these tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you anticipate the tears?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would thought?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not feeling so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, seriously, I think I'm gonna barf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka Naoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka Naoki
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,T A N A K A  N A O K I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to let you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let go of you, Tanaka Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,TA NA KA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,TA NA KA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,NA O KI
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, well, Yama-chan, thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that still not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't even heard Tanaka's response!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka's... HEY! LET ME GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I DON'T WANNA QUIT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, someone's gonna get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I DON'T WANT TO LEAVE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU CAN'T MAKE ME!! I WON'T DO IT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta make this your last show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,LET ME STAY LONGER, PLEASE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, no one wants to see this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I HAVEN'T DONE ANYTHING TO DESERVE THIS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'M NOT LEAVING
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, yeah, I mean, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But leaving the entire industry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- That certainly happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It turned out that it's not the show he's retiring from...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting next week, let's do our best as a foursome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,WAIT!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting next week, let's do our best as a foursome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,WAIT!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,HOUSEI AIN'T
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,QUITTIN' SHOWBIZ~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All you out there in TV land, did I scare ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I let two year pass, bided my time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,AND I GOTCHA FOR THE 16th TIME!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Housei will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,NOT! Be leaving Gaki no Tsukai NOR show business!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,NOT QUITTING NOT QUITTING
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:19:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,NOT QUITTING~!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And now he does his skit, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's gotta be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Can that bald guy even sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At least get rid of the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:19:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's super quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His Japanese was a bit shaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The bald guy doesn't even have his mic up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so focused on the lip-sync that he forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,HOUSEI AIN'T QUITTING
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,NOT QUITTING SHOWBIZ, NOT QUITTING GAKI
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:21:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,AND DEFINITELY NOT RAKUGO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, always, LET ME STAY
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,HOUSEI AIN'T QUITTING!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow~ Always~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,LET ME STAY~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Long, long, too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Really shoulda picked up the pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\N- Doesn't he do one more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,HOLD IT RIGHT THERE YOU SUNOVABITCH
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\N- Doesn't he do one more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,HOLD IT RIGHT THERE YOU SUNOVABITCH
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard you were plannin' on retiring...\N- Yeah yeah yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And came all the way down here from Hokkaido!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Moriman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you say you're NOT quitting?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cuz of YOU that we had to wake up at 6 this morning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't sit in that traffic jam for nothin'!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.91,0:22:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your freakin' problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Cue card says "Hamada-san, if you please"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.71,0:22:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And?\N- Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,BURDOCK BEATDOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta fight, it's the only way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll win this time, you'll win this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.18,0:22:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta fight!! It'll be easier if you fight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:22:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't run away!! There's no way out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:23:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight her!\N- Don't run away!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit her, You gotta hit her!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hit the crew!! Stop hitting the crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.31,0:23:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If we had known you hated burdock so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe the staff could've used something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I went after Takasu and Yanaoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.08,0:23:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,

